{"tid":566739,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼城前足球教練性侵犯多名兒童及少年球員　被利物浦皇家法院判監31年","createTime":"2018-02-20T08:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T09:45:58.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae0d188710cbb14f7c6f9863b781f9917601efe","tid":566739,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:02:57.000Z","msg":"更新日期：2018-02-20 12:24<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.independent.co.uk/s3fs-public/styles/story_large/public/thumbnails/image/2017/01/16/11/barry-bennell-bbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.independent.co.uk%2Fs3fs-public%2Fstyles%2Fstory_large%2Fpublic%2Fthumbnails%2Fimage%2F2017%2F01%2F16%2F11%2Fbarry-bennell-bbc.jpg&h=908243b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n    英國利物浦皇家法院（Liverpool Crown Court）當地時間周一（19日）裁定英國前足球教練本奈爾（Barry Bennell）50項性侵兒童及少年罪名成立，判監31年。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，現年64歲的本奈爾1979年至1991年於克魯（Crewe Alexandra）及<span style=\"color: red;\">曼城（Manchester City）足球俱樂部任職期間</span>，性侵12名8至15歲的男童或少年球員。<br />\n<br />\n法官戈德斯通（Clement Goldstone）判刑時形容本奈爾為「魔鬼的化身」，譴責他「偷走了孩子的童年和天真」，給受害者造成無法磨滅的心理陰影。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名受害者伍德沃德（Andy Woodward）表示：「本奈爾沒有對任何人表示懊悔或歉意。我為自己勇敢說出這一切而感到自豪，如果我沒有這麼做，我們今天都不會站在這裏。」"},{"pid":"a95c1180225dfff62caafa53903d80c30692f6c9","tid":566739,"uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:04:55.000Z","msg":"死利狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68c0643b4dd64ee227781a7d0bb415625a3f09f","tid":566739,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:22:49.000Z","msg":"對小孩子做這種事是世界上最差勁的人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/162210_0412c29576c708cf0155e8de242169b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F162210_0412c29576c708cf0155e8de242169b1.jpg&h=ee2fcc21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f172a4907e63a414c54cee478d593d99e56482ff","